# Project intake workflow

Infer-first brief intake, then plan/implement separation. **Full steps:** [project-intake/SKILL.md](../skills/project-intake/SKILL.md).

## When required

Greenfield, new feature without brief, create plan, design/mockup, scaffold — unless: implement-plan, scoped fix/refactor, `skip intake`, or matching brief exists in `.cursor/plans/_briefs/`.

## Flow

0. **Prompt refinement** (when `intake.prompt_refinement` ≠ off and hook routes `[route:prompt-refinement]`): [prompt-refinement/SKILL.md](../skills/prompt-refinement/SKILL.md) → structured prompt → user approval
1. Read [project.defaults.yaml](../config/project.defaults.yaml) + [project.intake-fields.yaml](../config/project.intake-fields.yaml)
2. Infer: user prompt → repo signals → config defaults → AskQuestion for gaps
3. Save brief: `.cursor/plans/_briefs/{slug}.brief.md` ([template](../plans/_templates/project-brief.template.md))
4. Route skill: design → [design-intake](../skills/design-intake/SKILL.md); plan → [implementation-plan](../skills/implementation-plan/SKILL.md); scaffold → [module-scaffolder](../skills/module-scaffolder/SKILL.md)
5. Plan: `.cursor/plans/features/{slug}.plan.md` — get approval before code
6. Implement: plan body read-only; only `todos[].status`; verify per [verification.md](../plans/_shared/verification.md)

Registry: [registry.json](../skills/skills-router/registry.json). Options: [intake-canonical-options.md](../plans/_shared/intake-canonical-options.md).
